Text: Haven't heard these guys in years. Great albums. But can someone seed. I'm at 56% and steady for a day.

Thank you for your contributions, esp. Jan Akkerman. His talent is prodigious. I'm glad to appreciate this music so late in life. And, please re-seed Flock. I look forward to hearing their music again. Love from the US.

Geen flauw idee wat ik download. Ik zie wel dat Jan Akkerman er deel van uit maakt.
Nieuwsgierig dus.
